195+1082+1018=3295次错误），recommendationservice（915次错误），checkoutservice（6次错误）。错误信息一致：'dial tcp 10.233.54.177:3550: connect: connection refused'\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"作为入口服务，frontend三个实例返回大量HTTP 500错误（1707+1546+1448=4701次），因无法连接ProductCatalogService导致服务不可用，响应时间从正常11-14秒降至0.2秒左右（Fast Fail模式）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"订单处理延迟显著异常：正常152118ms → 异常52388ms（延迟倍数0.34），显示快速失败模式，因无法获取商品信息导致订单处理失败\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键分析要点：\n\n### 1. **根因确认**\n- **ProductCatalogService** 是明确的根因服务，所有调用它的上游服务都出现相同的连接拒绝错误\n- 错误指向同一IP地址和端口：`10.233.54.177:3550`\n- 这是调用链中最下游的服务，直接影响整个系统\n\n### 2. **故障传播模式**\n- **直接受害者**：Frontend、RecommendationService、CheckoutService\n- **故障模式**：Fast Fail（快速失败），响应时间显著缩短\n- **错误一致性**：所有服务报告相同的连接拒绝错误\n\n### 3. **支持共识的理由**\n- trace数据与log、metric数据高度一致，都指向ProductCatalogService问题\n- 错误模式明确：端口连接被拒绝，而非服务内部错误\n- 影响范围广泛：所有依赖商品目录的服务都受影响\n\n**结论**：我完全支持当前共识，ProductCatalogService的端口配置错误或服务不可用是本次故障的根本原因。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nDISAGREED\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nAGREED", "log_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "b9539d8e-345", "component": "productcatalogservice", "reason": "connection refused and transport error while dialing tcp 10.233.54.177:3550 causing service unavailability", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LogSearch(productcatalogservice)", "observation": "Found transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.54.177:3550: connect: connection refused errors"}, {"step": 2, "action": "LoadMetrics(productcatalogservice)", "o